'''Easthaven''' was one of the larger settlements that made up the collective [[Ten Towns]] of [[Icewind Dale]]. While it was once a small shanty town, Easthaven had a long a storied history that developed as it grew into a more and more prosperous trading community.{{Cite adventurers league/Terror in Ten Towns|3}}

{{Quote|The area of Easthaven is but one of many tiny, frigid villages clinging to survival. They endure, but it is a hard life, and the only war that comes to Easthaven is the battle against the elements.|[[Everard]], Trusted Sword, [[Order of the Broken Blade]], [[Eleint]], [[1281 DR]].}}

